CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 1, 1958, pg. 14, reads: "Diplomas Bring Smiles - Smiling after receiving diplomas at Herron Hill Junior High School are Henry Harper (center) and (left to right), Raymond Talley and Melvin Davis, winners also of the Ben Franklin Awards in Graphic Arts, and Michael Tyler and Alfred Diggs, Gerwig Award recipients. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of five young men, left to right: Raymond Talley, Melvin Davis, Henry Harper, Michael Tyler, and Alfred Diggs, at Herron Hill Junior High School graduation
